《'''奧班農訴NCAA案'''》是美國的一起[[競爭法|反壟斷]][[集體訴訟|集體訴訟]]。

==案情==
本案第一原告為[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]畢業的原[[加州大學洛杉磯分校棕熊隊|校隊]]籃球員{{link-en|愛德華·奧班農|Ed O'Bannon}}。他因為不滿[[藝電|藝電]]在《{{link-en|NCAA籃球系列|NCAA Basketball series}}》電子遊戲中使用了他的肖像，卻沒有向他支付肖像權使用費（因为加大洛杉磯分校所屬的[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]（NCAA）禁止向學生運動員發放除獎學金以外的任何收益），而將NCAA、[[藝電|藝電]]、以及{{link-en|校際體育特許授權公司|Collegiate Licensing Company}}告上法庭。奧班農主張：學生運動員在結束運動生涯以後，如果NCAA使用其肖像作牟利之用，大學生運動員應該獲得部份收益<ref>{{cite web | last= Streeter | first= Kurt | date= July 22, 2009 | url= http://www.latimes.com/sports/college/basketball/la-sp-videogames-lawsuit22-2009jul22,0,6741087.story | title= Former UCLA star Ed O'Bannon leads suit against NCAA over use of images | work= [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | access-date= 2020-12-23 | archive-date= 2009-07-25 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090725160319/http://www.latimes.com/sports/college/basketball/la-sp-videogames-lawsuit22-2009jul22,0,6741087.story | dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | date= July 21, 2009 | url= http://sports.espn.go.com/ncb/news/story?id=4346470 | title= Former Bruin O'Bannon sues NCAA | agency= [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | work= ESPN.go.com | accessdate= 2020-12-23 | archive-date= 2015-09-28 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150928173633/http://sports.espn.go.com/ncb/news/story?id=4346470 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。但NCAA則主張：學生運動員獲得任何此類收益，都與大學聯賽的「業餘性質」不符<ref>{{cite news|last=Pierce|first=Charles P.|title=How It Ends|date=June 20, 2014|work=grantland.com|url=http://grantland.com/features/ncaa-amateurism-lawsuit-mark-emmert/|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QU7lsHvJ?url=http://grantland.com/features/ncaa-amateurism-lawsuit-mark-emmert/|archivedate=2014-06-21|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。訴訟開始後，先後有20名前大學運動員加入原告奧班農一方<ref name="espn_05232014">{{cite news|title=NCAA antitrust trial set for June 9|date=May 23, 2014|work=ESPN.com|url=http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/10975452/judge-orders-antitrust-suit-vs-ncaa-go-trial-next-month|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Pni8lkvU?url=http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/10975452/judge-orders-antitrust-suit-vs-ncaa-go-trial-next-month|archivedate=2014-05-24|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年8月8日，[[美國加利福尼亞北區聯邦地區法院|加州北區聯邦地區法院]]裁定：NCAA拒絕和學生運動員分享肖像權收益的做法，已經違反了美國的反壟斷法<ref>"[T]he Court finds that this restraint does violate antitrust law." p.98, ''O'Bannon v. NCAA'', N.D. Cal., Aug. 8, 2014.</ref>。而本案的另外兩個被告[[藝電|藝電]]和{{link-en|校際體育特許授權公司|Collegiate Licensing Company}}，則在宣判之前和原告達成的價值4000萬美元的庭外和解：超過10萬名肖像曾在《[[NCAA美式足球系列|NCAA美式足球系列]]》或《{{link-en|NCAA籃球系列|NCAA Basketball series}}》中出現的前大學運動員，每人最多可獲得四千美元的賠償<ref>{{cite news|last=Munson|first=Lester|title=NCAA athletes get their day in court|date=June 8, 2014|work=ESPN.com|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/otl/story/_/id/11045682/ed-obannon-lawsuit-ncaa-paying-players-set-begin|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QG1pblAE?url=http://espn.go.com/espn/otl/story/_/id/11045682/ed-obannon-lawsuit-ncaa-paying-players-set-begin|archivedate=2014-06-11|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Farrey|first=Tom|title=Players, game makers settle for $40M|date=May 31, 2014|work=ESPN.com|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/otl/story/_/id/11010455/college-athletes-reach-40-million-settlement-ea-sports-ncaa-licensing-arm|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QG21vZnw?url=http://espn.go.com/espn/otl/story/_/id/11010455/college-athletes-reach-40-million-settlement-ea-sports-ncaa-licensing-arm|archivedate=2014-06-11|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

NCAA事後提出了上訴<ref name="jessop_03132015">{{cite news|last=Jessop|first=Alicia|title=Pay for play: NCAA schools keep eye on legal cases|date=March 13, 2015|work=CNBC.com|url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/102503779?__source=yahoo%7Cfinance%7Cinline%7Cstory%7Cstory&par=yahoo&doc=102532149|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XHhQfNMF?url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/102503779?__source=yahoo%7Cfinance%7Cinline%7Cstory%7Cstory&par=yahoo&doc=102532149|archivedate=2015-03-25|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但被[[美國最高法院|美國最高法院]]駁回<ref>{{cite news|last=Edelman|first=Marc|title=By Denying Certiorari In O'Bannon v. NCAA, The Supreme Court Aids Future Reform To College Sports|date=October 7, 2016|work=Forbes|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/marcedelman/2016/10/07/by-denying-certiorari-in-obannon-v-ncaa-the-supreme-court-aids-future-reform-to-college-sports/#4f677172270f|accessdate=2020-12-23|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903130829/https://www.forbes.com/sites/marcedelman/2016/10/07/by-denying-certiorari-in-obannon-v-ncaa-the-supreme-court-aids-future-reform-to-college-sports/#4f677172270f|dead-url=no}}</ref>。各級法院更要求NCAA支付4220萬美元訴訟費<ref>{{cite court|litigants=O'Bannon v. NCAA | opinion=No. 16-15803 | court=9th Cir.| date=June 29, 2018|url=https://cdn.ca9.uscourts.gov/datastore/memoranda/2018/06/29/16-15803.pdf}}</ref>。

==事後==
事後NCAA向藝電發出通牒：不准藝電在電子遊戲中使用NCAA的品牌或運動員肖像。藝電因此被迫停止開發《[[NCAA美式足球系列|NCAA美式足球系列]]》。

